title: tkm
lyrics:
Will you ever
Say you love me
Say you want me
Or whatever?
I have wondered

If you need me

It doesn't always

Seem like it



But after all is fine

That you need this much time

It’s obvious what you think

I understand



Will you ever

Care about me

Ask about me

Talk whenever?



I've been waiting

Really struggling

Since forever

To make you smile



But if you say goodbye

I won't be asking why

It’s obvious what you think

About us



I'm tired of everything

Let me know

Oh, do you feel the same?
